We cant use "IBMOem" here.The name "Oem" is defined in the ComputerSystem schema, but "IBMOem" is not.
But we can set "IBMOem" as a subobject of "Oem", example:

"Oem": {
    "@odata.type": "#OemComputerSystem.Oem",
    "IBMOem": {
      "@odata.type": "#OemComputerSystem.IBMOem",
      "LampTest": true
    }
  }

